---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Maitan Hub | Colophon" sidebarLayout={false}>
  <!-- Sidebar Menu (Anchors) -->
  <div slot="sidebar">
    <a href="/" class="nav-item mb-4">
      <span class="nav-text">← voltar</span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <a href="/colophon/design-system" class="nav-item"
        ><span class="nav-text">design system</span></a
      >
      <a href="/policy" class="nav-item"
        ><span class="nav-text">políticas</span></a
      >
      <a href="#licenca" class="nav-item"
        ><span class="nav-text">licença</span></a
      >
      <a href="#historico" class="nav-item"
        ><span class="nav-text">histórico</span></a
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="article-header">
    <span class="category-link">bastidores</span>
    <h1 class="display-title">colophon</h1>
    <div class="meta-date">Atualizado em Novembro 2025</div>
  </header>

  <div class="article-grid">
    <div class="text-column">
      <p class="body-text first-paragraph">
        Os bastidores deste jardim digital. Ferramentas, escolhas e a filosofia
        por trás de cada pixel. Este site é um exercício contínuo de redução e
        estrutura.
      </p>

      <div class="section-divider">***</div>

      <p class="body-text">
        Para detalhes visuais e componentes, consulte o <a
          href="/colophon/design-system"
          class="underline hover:text-vermilion transition-colors"
          >Design System</a
        >. Para questões legais e de privacidade, veja nossas <a
          href="/policy"
          class="underline hover:text-vermilion transition-colors">Políticas</a
        >.
      </p>

      <!-- Footer Info -->
      <div
        class="space-y-8 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 mt-16"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4" id="licenca">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Licença</h2>
          <p class="body-text" style="font-size: 1rem;">
            Conteúdo sob licença <a
              href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-300 dark:decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-2 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors"
              >CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a
            >. Código no <a
              href="https://github.com/luanmaitan/maitan"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-300 dark:decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-2 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors"
              >GitHub</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4" id="historico">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Histórico</h2>
          <p class="body-text" style="font-size: 1rem;">
            Acompanhe a evolução do projeto através do changelog.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/colophon/changelog"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-medium text-neutral-900 dark:text-white hover:text-primary transition-colors group"
          >
            Ver Changelog
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="16"
              height="16"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
            >
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Marginalia -->
    <div class="marginalia-col">
      <div class="sidenote" style="top: 0;">
        <span class="note-label">Navegação</span>
        Explore o <a href="/colophon/design-system" class="underline"
          >Design System</a
        > completo.
      </div>

      <div class="sidenote" style="top: 150px;">
        <span class="note-label">Legal</span>
        Leia nossas <a href="/policy" class="underline"
          >Políticas de Privacidade</a
        >.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
```
